{"type": "article", "id": 30226, "title": "柔软的太阳能灯具", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-27T22:59:05Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 39, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160727220923doKFh30T7seg1rzH.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>当人们把“柔软”和“灯光”联系在一起时，通常表达的是光线的明暗。不过用它来形容 <a href=\"http://www.solight-design.com/#solarpuff\" rel=\"nofollow\">Solight</a> 这款名为 Solar Puff 太阳能灯具的话，就是真的在说它摸上去非常柔软了。这些小巧的正方体灯具由织物制成，能够压成厚度仅为 6 毫米的薄薄一片，便于随身携带。灯具上方设有太阳能板，在阳光下充满 8 小时之后能够连续使用 8 到 12 小时。这是它的<a href=\"http://www.solight-design.com/storeall/solarpuff\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 30 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160727221621P9JpaD6ym7hSTHUR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160727221621HnGRm5ebdywrCxJQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160727221621ePtZik1BXKJ5Sr9m.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160727221621qOU3xy2SsPeYcz0N.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}